OL,3,CHospital restricts visiting after
OL,4,Coutbreak of norovirus
OL,6,FA hospital in Surrey has brought in
OL,7,Fvisiting restrictions on its wards
OL,8,Fafter an outbreak of norovirus.
OL,10,FSurrey & Sussex Healthcare NHS Trust,
OL,11,Fwhich runs the East Surrey Hospital in
OL,12,FRedhill, said visiting was being
OL,13,Ftemporarily restricted until Monday on
OL,14,Fmost of its wards.
OL,16,FThey've also asked anyone who has
OL,17,Fexperienced diarrhoea or vomiting in
OL,18,Fthe last 48 hours not to attend the
OL,19,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
