OL,3,CHospital restricts visiting after
OL,4,Coutbreak of norovirus
OL,6,FIn a notice on their website, they
OL,7,Fsaid the change doesn't apply to
OL,8,FPaediatrics, Maternity of End of Life
OL,9,Fpatients.
OL,11,FIn addition, patients in the Emergency
OL,12,FDepartment are allowed one visitor per
OL,13,Fday.
